溫尼菲爾德二世]]也表示對KN-08型[[洲際彈道飛彈|洲際彈道飛彈]]感到擔心，並認為北韓的飛彈發展程度比預期還快速。KN-08型飛彈在2012年的閱兵典禮中首次亮相，由16個輪子的車輛運載展示，但也被部分人士懷疑真實性。<ref>{{cite web |last=Marcus |first=Jonathan |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-17867174 |title=BBC News - New ICBM missiles at North Korea parade 'fake' |publisher=Bbc.co.uk |date=2012-04-27 |accessdate=2012-10-09 |archive-date=2012-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120824074219/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-17867174 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.defensenews.com/article/20120630/DEFREG03/306300005/U-N-Report-Suggest-N-Korean-Parade-Missiles-Possibly-Fakes |title=U.N. Report Suggest N. Korean Parade Missiles Possibly Fakes | Defense News |publisher=defensenews.com |date=2012-10-05 |accessdate=2012-10-09 |archive-date=2013-01-21 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20130121220445/http://www.defensenews.com/article/20120630/DEFREG03/306300005/U-N-Report-Suggest-N-Korean-Parade-Missiles-Possibly-Fakes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author=The Associated Press |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/story/2012/04/26/north-korea-missile-analysts-fake.html |title=North Korean missiles dismissed as fakes - World - CBC News |publisher=Cbc.ca |date=2012-04-26 |accessdate=2012-10-09 |archive-date=2012-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120615081342/http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/story/2012/04/26/north-korea-missile-analysts-fake.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>此外，哈格爾還透露美國打算再部署AN/TPY-2雷達於位在日本的防禦系統上，此舉可讓預警能力提升，且加強追蹤任何北韓導彈的飛行路線。第一部AN/TPY-2雷達被安裝於[[日本|日本]]北部，2006年開始啟用。目前預計第二部將會裝置在日本中部，但幾個月內還不能完全運作。<ref name="speechid1759"/><ref name="defense-update1">{{cite news|title=US Reinforcing Pacific Defenses to Counter North Korean Threats|url=http://defense-update.com/20130406_us-reinforcing-pacific-defenses-to-counter-north-korean-threats.html|date=2013-04-06|accessdate=2013-04-06|publisher=Defense-Update.com|archive-date=2013-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130409132558/http://defense-update.com/20130406_us-reinforcing-pacific-defenses-to-counter-north-korean-threats.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

